# Language Policy Template

This file is a template. Copy it to `rules/language.md` to activate language enforcement for WORKTREE_NOTES.md.

The hook (`hooks/check-worktree-notes-lang.js`) reads `$AGENTS_CONFIG_DIR/rules/language.md`.
Copying this `.example` file is not sufficient — `rules/language.md` must exist.

## Conversation
<!-- Set your conversation language here (English or Japanese) -->

## Planning Artifacts
<!-- Set your planning artifact language -->

## Commit Messages
<!-- Commit messages: always English -->

## Code
<!-- Source code and config file messages/comments: English -->

## Documentation

<!-- Configure language enforcement for WORKTREE_NOTES.md staging sections.
     IMPORTANT: DOCS_LANG_HISTORY consistency matters — history.md is append-only
     and hard to retroactively change. Choose your language once and stick with it. -->

````docs-lang
# DOCS_LANG_HISTORY: language for ## History Notes in WORKTREE_NOTES.md
# Valid values: english | japanese | any
# "any" disables enforcement (no CJK check)
DOCS_LANG_HISTORY=any

# DOCS_LANG_CHANGELOG_PUBLIC: language for ## Changelog Notes in public repos
DOCS_LANG_CHANGELOG_PUBLIC=any

# DOCS_LANG_CHANGELOG_PRIVATE: language for ## Changelog Notes in private repos
DOCS_LANG_CHANGELOG_PRIVATE=any
````
